What is their job?
How many hours a day do they work?
How much do they make in an hour?
Write down one challenge about their job
$whoswho_body$
WHERE lesson_id = '1n8wS0X-dXAw9sfQuLFgsMg_kNvACph3cT4yd9p2i1eg'
